Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:02.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:05.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:14.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't disappeared yet. {from Hirono heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, this is who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:08.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you read it, you'll be yourself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:13.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay leaving her by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She'll have to deal with the rest of it on her own.{She will be on her own for the rest of it.}{She have to solve the rest of the problem herself, etc} {She'll have to solve the rest of the problem by herself. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:20.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've warned you not to get too involved with Chihiro. {involved as on getting in deeper relationship} {I warned you about not getting too involved with Chihiro. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:25.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've warned you to be prepared if you wanted to be with her too. {I've also warned you to be prepared if you wanted to be with her. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro lost four years worth of her memories. {Chihiro lost four years worth of her memories. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:35.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the only things that remain are a few scattered, unrecognizable memories...{Though the memories were just some subtle unconnected images that remains.}{check} {Shini; How about, "The only things that remain are a few scattered, unrecognizable memories."}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If she takes some time and reads her diary again, {If she takes some time to read her diary again, - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,she should return to the most recent her. {Saint- She should return to her normal self.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just something that has happened many times. {It's just something that has happened many times before. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It will happen again in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:54.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And then, as time passes, the pain of her losing memories will only become worse. {And then, as time goes on, the pain of losing her memories will only get worse. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:57.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then all the more, this is the time someone should be with her. {That's the reason why someone should be with her during that time. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The pain that will become worse will be your pain, Renji. {The pain that will be getting worse will be yours, Renji. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:11.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've warned you not to get too involved with her. {Saint- That's why I warned you not to get too involved with her.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:13.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:16.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can still back away now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro right now doesn't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to disappear, then now is the time.{If you want to disappear, then this is the right time.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right. {Saint- Something's not right (Typically how one would casually say it)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Tsutsumi speaking. {name check[Shini; Correct.]}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai? It's me, Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you meet with me for a bit? {Saint- Could you accompany me for a while?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:35.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... will change even if I read these! {Even if I read these, nothing will change! - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will only return to those same days again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:42.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating that same, empty daily life. {Repeating that empty life, from day to day. - megu} {Saint- Repeating the same empty life, daily.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:44.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to continue writing in this diary as I always have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:53.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Writing the same things in my diary... Why do I have to keep on writing them?! {Megane: as in writing the same thing over and over again?} {Saint- Writing the same things in my diary... Do I have to carry on writing them?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better if it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Being who I am, it would be better if it ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't be calm without touching the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:11.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just bring Hirono to accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask for something impossible; he is swamped with work. {Don't ask for something impossible. He's swamped with work right now. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going well with you and Hirono?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,G-Going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My relationship with Hirono-senpai is more like that of siblings. {My relationship with Hirono-senpai is more like that of being siblings. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think... {It's not what you think... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:35.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually asking about it from the "siblings" relationship perspective. {Actually, I was asking about it from the "being siblings" perspective. - megu}{That didn't get too well... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:42.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When she was alive, my mother used to be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She had that bright sparkle about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanted to make a movie with that kind of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Bright sparkle? {maybe other words isntead of bright, shine? sparkle?}{[Shini; "Shined" perhaps?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kei-chan has that bright sparkle too. {I think Kei-chan is sparkling brightly as well. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:05.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's not the same sparkle I saw in you the first time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:09.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if something had happened between you and Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like he's so distant from me. {He just feels so distant to me. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized it, he is in some place I can't reach anymore. {When I realized it, he was like in some place that I can't reach anymore. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:19.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:20.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not only Hirono-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are working really hard for your dream, Tsutsumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And even my younger sister has started writing a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:32.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And with her condition, that is almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:36.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But yet this injury has ground me to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sparkle, being like this. { - megu}{Me being like this can't sprakle.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But those aren't the only things that make you worry, right? {But that's not the only thing that's making you worry, right? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:46.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I look through the camera's viewfinder, I can see everything.{When I see through the camera finder, I'll know everything}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! {[Shini; Whenever people say that, I always equate it with a colloquial greeting like "Hey there" or some equivalent. Yahoo in English however doesn't quite sound the same as in Japanese so I recommend changing it.]}{I think "Yaho~!" would be fine. - megu} {Saint- Maybe a good equivalent would be Yoohoo?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed it with this. {[Shini; DANGO wat.]}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,See? A telephone card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I got it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't be getting strange mails or calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't be able to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess that's the drawback, huh? {Ah, I guess that's the only drawback. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about standing you up last Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine now since you came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.{This isn't like you.}{Saint- }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:43.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you should send your future career survey in quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, they'll call your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What did you write on yours, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should write "going to the university" first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How about being a manga author?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'm going to let my parents know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:01.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If they found out about my current work, they'd make me stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:05.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad doesn't approve of what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was the one who left home.{Well, I was the one who went away from the house.}{Well, I was the one who moved away from our house. - megu}{Saint- }
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious of your freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be told that by you. {I don't want to heard that from you. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:15.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:20.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you seem to show that feeling of being carefree everywhere you go, don't you?{ [Shini; Figure of speech. Sorta. Needs rewording I think...]} {Well, you look as if you have that aura of being carefree everywhere you go, don't you? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:21.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My freedom is nothing but an empty shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:30.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For Hirono-kun, your freedom is the freedom to do something you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:36.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To go through a lot of hardships and harsh times while pursuing your dream...{Go through a lot of hardship and harsh times while pusuing your dream...}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,is a very fulfilling kind of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yours isn't an empty one either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:46.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have to think about a lot of things, it doesn't allow you to do anything else.{You have to think a lot of things, just don't let you do anything else.} {It's just since you're busy with a lot of things, you don't have the time to do anything else. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:52.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it so much just makes your head hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can just throw them all away and run if it's too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:00.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are free to choose whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:04.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's also okay to just throw them away.{That's why choosing to just throwing them away is fine too.}{ megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:08.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You want to run away together with me? {That's right... Would you like to run away together with me? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To somewhere far away where nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have chosen, so I have certain responsibilities. {Saint- I have chosen so I have certain responsibilities.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:24.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just run away when you have already chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:30.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten me involved too, so don't run away from me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's something that I'd want to say "never happened".{I guess it's something that I really want to just say "it never happened".}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:39.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:45.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, now I think that I can take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, those were just my thoughts. {Well, those were just my thoughts. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:56.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I feel at ease when I'm with you too, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:10:01.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only during the limited time I'm together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:02.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:05.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:05.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like what?{Say something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You write shoujo manga right? {girly comics}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any romantic lines for such moments? {Don't you have any romantic lines for moments like these? - megu} {Saint- Don't you have any romantic lines for such a moment?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to let you go anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That was lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Very plain.
