Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that for another situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, are you really a pro-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bad at expressing my ad-lib...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not on paper, I can't bring out those words. {If it's not on paper, I can't make the words out. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:16.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then bring me to somewhere that has your paper... {Then bring me to somewhere that's similar. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard of this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, it was an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,An experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:31.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,An experiment to see what a baby would first say if it was brought up without talking to anyone. {An experiment to see what a baby would say if it was brought up without talking to anyone. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The baby wouldn't say anything, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's half correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Half correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:42.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The baby indeed wouldn't say anything, but the baby would die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:49.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But in my case, I didn't die and I can talk too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:51.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:57.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, will you only look at me?{Hirono-kun, whatever it is, can you only look towards me?}{Whatever it is Hirono-kun, can you look directly at me? - megu} {Saint- }
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will only look at you. {Alright, I'll look directly at you. - megu} {Saint- Yes, I will only look at you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:05.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear from someone's heart anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is this about Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:15.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:22.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro has talked about nothing but putting things to an end. {Saint- All Chihiro has been talking about is nothing but putting things to an end.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared for her. {check, might be "I'm scared for her" too}{[Shini; Sounds right.]}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:30.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's just normal for you to feel like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even the painful feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know when one feels loneliness?  {check because they might be talking why is Chihiro feels lonely and not generally}{[Shini; General statement.]}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When you are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's basically just a result of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's something more to the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:46.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because... it's enjoyable? {[Shini; Doesn't quite sound right...needs to be reworded perhaps?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:51.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Learning how to enjoy life after feeling loneliness for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:56.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like learning about sadness after feeling happiness for the first time. {Changed "unhappiness" into "sadness" - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:57.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:01.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This world is filled with things that have two sides to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like a laughable tragedy of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:09.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Like water, you two have stepped into this realm of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What else can I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied after saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel better now after saying that to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:26.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why... didn't you tell me about Chihiro's condition sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I did give you a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:30.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You should've been able to stop us from seeing each other too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:34.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right. Perhaps I just wanted to see the result. {I guess you're right. Maybe I just wanted to see the result. - megu} {Saint- Maybe you're right, but maybe I just wanted to see the result.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:39.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see if someone like me could accomplish what I had hoped to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:45.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I know the answer as to what you and Chihiro should do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:46.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:49.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:54.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Go and read Chihiro's novel carefully. {Go and read Chihiro's novel carefully. - megu}{gah, I had to look up "peruse" in a dictionary for a bit there... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:58.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And then think about why she wrote a novel like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:07.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl started to practice painting the next day after the wedding ceremony."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Despite the wedding ceremony, there was only one human on this side of the paintings."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:16.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"So, she started painting herself on the paintings."{That's why she started to paint herself into the pictures.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She painted everything in the pictures."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In that painted world, there were two humans smiling at each other." {In that painted world, there were two humans smiling at each other. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She felt strange when she looked at herself in the pictures."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She didn't really understand that feeling."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:36.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"However, she continued with her curiosity."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is only one in the world." {The girl was alone in the world. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the god of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Want to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I made some cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like them. {Saint- I hope you like them.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:54.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hospitality, Renji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:00.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that you were someone older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then just use whichever is easier for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, please let me call you as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will return...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:12.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely return to the previous me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:19.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote a novel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nearly to the end of the story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have to continue writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just resume writing only when you feel like it.{Resume writing it only when you feel like it.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:35.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me again when the time comes, Renji-kun? {Will you help me again when the time comes, Renji-kun? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have read it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:13.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I... can really come back to the me that you know, Renji-kun. {I... I can really return to the me that you know, Renji-kun. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:17.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you will be able to capture the spirit of Chihiro once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:25.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm just like the previous me, who loved Renji-kun a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:29.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:33.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:39.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've never had someone say, "I love you" to me before. {Well, I've never had anyone say "I love you" to me before. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But in the diary, it said that I confessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is actually something from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And it's more like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's really an "unofficial" confession... {Isn't that supposed to be "an unofficial confession"? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:55.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The word "love" was written many times in the diary, so I just assumed that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:02.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just move ahead too fast...? {Did I move ahead too fast...? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget what I just said. {Saint- Please forget what I just said.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've already heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:14.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,These past four years... {These past four years... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:22.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For four years, I have been in a standstill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:25.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would've better if I had just gone to a dead end. {I thought it would've been better if I just went to a dead end. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:29.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything and I have nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was just standing there waiting for the time to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:37.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that it would stop. {Saint- I was hoping that it would stop.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:42.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It felt so painful reading about me being like that. {Saint- It felt so painful reading about me being like that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:48.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But after meeting Renji-kun, everything became brighter. {Saint- But after meeting Renji-kun, everything became brighter.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:54.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Every day became happy moments and just by reading them, I felt really warm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:18:01.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even from this page to this one, each small bit is a part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what a memory is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:14.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:20.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If memories change, does the personality change too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:26.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Or does it stay as it is, but only what you remember changes? {Or will the personality stay as it is, but only the things that would change are your memories? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:32.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The exact personality might change, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:36.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think the personality of the real person will stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be glad if that is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I lost my memories four years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:48.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if the real me died that day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:56.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The same way I thought that the "me" while being with Renji-kun was already gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I started to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, Chihiro is Chihiro. {Saint- Whatever happens, Chihiro is Chihiro.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:12.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You neither died, nor did you turn into a different person. {You neither didn't die nor a different person.}{- megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:17.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro will always be the Chihiro I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so foolish, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:25.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way such a thing is true.{No way such thing is true.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that can be true. {Saint- There's no way that is true.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:55.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:59.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, damn, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro has already forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro can't remember anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:10.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:14.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that Chihiro's existence is weaker than sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That Chihiro's memories are duller than sand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way! {There's no way that is true! - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:24.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She met me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Laughed with me... {Laughed with me... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She even got angry and cried with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She is the Chihiro I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She is not a different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:41.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will never accept!{check [Shini; Okay.]}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:55.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:57.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This loneliness is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the god of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go wake up Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:12.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How about some sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:13.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I think...
